OL,3,CSadiq Khan on track for re-election as
OL,4,CLondon Mayor, according to poll
OL,6,FSadiq Khan is on course for a
OL,7,Flandslide re-election and
OL,8,Funprecedented third term as Mayor,
OL,9,Faccording to a new poll for ITV News,
OL,10,FLondon.
OL,12,FThe poll of 1,019 Londoners by
OL,13,FSurvation revealed the incumbent
OL,14,FLabour mayor on 44% of the vote, with
OL,15,Fhis Conservative rival, Susan Hall, on
OL,16,F26% - eighteen points behind.
OL,18,FThe Liberal Democrats' Rob Blackie,
OL,19,Fand Zoe Garbett, the Green Party
OL,20,Fcandidate, are level on 7%, with
OL,21,FReform UK's Howard Cox on 5%.
