OL,3,CSadiq Khan on track for re-election as
OL,4,CLondon Mayor, according to poll
OL,6,FIf those results are replicated in the
OL,7,FMayoral Election on 2nd May, Mr Khan
OL,8,Fwill become the first mayor in history
OL,9,Fto be elected for a third time in
OL,10,Foffice at City Hall.
OL,12,FThe May election will be held using
OL,13,Fthe first-past-the-post system for the
OL,14,Ffirst time, meaning voters will no
OL,15,Flonger be able to vote for a second
OL,16,Fpreference candidate.
OL,18,FMr Khan also leads Ms Hall across all
OL,19,Fage brackets ` except for voters aged
OL,20,F65+, where the Conservative has a 30-
OL,21,Fpoint lead.
