OL,3,CSadiq Khan on track for re-election as
OL,4,CLondon Mayor, according to poll
OL,6,FDespite strong polling numbers for the
OL,7,Fmayor, the race for City Hall is
OL,8,Ftighter than the race for Number 10 at
OL,9,Fthe upcoming General Election ` where
OL,10,FLabour are on course to pick up 52% of
OL,11,Fthe capital's votes, compared to the
OL,12,FTories' 21%.
OL,14,FBoth leading mayoral candidates have
OL,15,Fsmall positive approval ratings ` Ms
OL,16,FHall is on +5%, while Mr Khan is on
OL,17,F+4%.
